import Vue, { createApp } from 'vue'
import Vuesax from 'vuesax'
import 'vuesax/dist/vuesax.css'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'


createApp(App).mount('#app')

Vue.config.productionTip = false

Vue.use(Vuesax, {})

new Vue({
  router,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
